OL,4,BMario Balotelli: Hellas Verona punished
OL,5,Bwith partial stadium closure for one
OL,6,Bgame
OL,7, Italian club Hellas Verona have been
OL,8, ordered to close part of their stadium
OL,9, for one game following the racist abuse
OL,10, of Mario Balotelli.
OL,12,FBrescia striker Balotelli kicked the
OL,13,Fball into the crowd and threatened to
OL,14,Fwalk off the pitch after being abused
OL,15,Fduring Sunday's 2-1 defeat at Verona.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Serie A's disciplinary
OL,18,Fcommission ordered the closure of the
OL,19,FPoltrone Est stand as punishment.
